data.description: Welcome to this stunning Ranch w/ 4 bedrooms, 3.5 baths, a finished basement, & an excellent location that combines the charm of country living w/ the convenience of city proximity. This open-concept home is brimming w/ storage space & offers a picturesque exterior w/ lush landscaping, a spacious driveway w/ a turn-around, a 2.5 car garage nestled on a generous 1.05-acre lot. As you step through the foyer, you'll notice the luxury vinyl flooring throughout. To the right, a formal office complete w/ a sliding barn door. Moving on, you'll enter the vaulted great room, enhanced w/ built-in features & transom windows that flood the home w/ natural light. The great room seamlessly connects to the kitchen, which boasts upgraded kitchen cabinets, crown molding, pull-out shelves, a walk-in pantry, under-cabinet lighting, Corian countertops, ample cabinetry & stainless steel appliances. The 1st floor is dedicated to all 4 bedrooms, starting w/ the master that features a WIC & an en-suite bath w/ a walk-in shower equipped w/ dual shower heads & a spacious vanity. 3 additional bedrooms share a full bath. Laundry room w/ built-ins & a powder room complete the main level. The basement offers multiple areas for relaxation & various activities & is roughed in for another kitchen area. A full bath completes the lower level. Enjoy warm summer evenings by the fire pit in the backyard, which backs to mature trees. A 1 year home warranty is included for peace of mind.
